            "title": "特朗普據悉計畫推出「創世使命」以促進美國AI發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普據悉計畫推出「創世使命」以促進美國AI發展\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8aCky3eYYd.DlfLGNn9Aiw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/a725ebe0-c5b8-11f0-9f7b-37a189879b08\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普據悉計畫推出「創世使命」以促進美國AI發展</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA-%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%96%E4%BD%BF%E5%91%BD-%E4%BB%A5%E4%BF%83%E9%80%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bai%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95-012701925.html",
