        {
            "title": "美國駐加拿大大使預計貿易談判將會重啟 但具體時間不確定",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Pete Hoekstra, the US ambassador to Canada.\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DBGJBHezq14Y7BPvGGREmg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d3864393aec3025c2973d8fc181dd9f5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>Pete Hoekstra</span>, the US ambassador to Canada.</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國駐渥太華大使表示，儘管上個月發生外交衝突，川普憤怒地中止了談判，但加拿大和美國仍有機會達成降低關稅的協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大使Pete Hoekstra周三在渥太華與製造商舉行的會議上表示，大約一個月前，兩國在解決某些貿易摩擦的有限範圍內的協議上取得進展。 他預測會談將會恢復，但他不確定具體時間。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國駐加拿大大使Pete Hoekstra。攝影：Al Drago/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P94nPaKLHzI_1ruWykcxBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3c8313bc84d5a8ec3df6c4b38435e6f8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國駐加拿大大使Pete Hoekstra。攝影：Al Drago/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我有一些建議，我認為可以重啟談判，但這並不容易，」他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自10月23日川普在Truth Social平台就一則爭議廣告表達不滿以來，兩國之間的會談一直處於停滯狀態。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-41d3fe50-bb94-3d47-883f-b935bb65bce5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hoekstra周三表示，加拿大必須接受與美國之間免稅貿易的時代已經結束這一事實。「肯定會有關稅，明白嗎？川普已經非常非常明確地表明了這一點，」Hoekstra說，他已鼓勵加拿大官員「與我們密切合作」，並「爭取進入美國所能提供的最低關稅等級」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump’s Canada Envoy Sees Trade Talks Resuming After Sudden Halt</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A7%90%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F-%E4%BD%86%E5%85%B7%E9%AB%94%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A-060238085.html",
